{"tid":2514380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国駐日大使館PO圖諷刺美國 反遭各方圍剿急删除","createTime":"2021-05-03T08:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T08:37:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e2489bfe5d82cc0b3fe99362a9feef12a58674d0","tid":2514380,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3519332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3519332&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=0bacf4c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3519332&h=91c79e45\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3519332</a><br />\n<br />\n中國駐日大使館近日在推特PO出諷刺美國的圖片，只見披著美國國旗的死神正敲著埃及大門，前面伊拉克、利比亞、敘利亞的門縫都流出血跡，不過旋即被各方批評「大使館到底在衝三小」、「感到一陣寒意襲來」，還有人仿照圖片畫出中國對待新疆、西藏、香港的模樣，中國駐日使館的貼文接著便刪除了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/05/03/phpK59TqR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F05%2F03%2FphpK59TqR.jpg&h=a0394cf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖擷自@GonzoTambourine推特）<br />\n<br />\n據《NHK》報導，從推特上可以看到，中國駐日大使館當時用日文寫著「這就是美國帶來的民主」，似乎是在嘲諷美國為了維持區域穩定而出兵的行為。事實上，中國政府近年來經常透過推特等社交平台向外國交流，但發文內容經常引起爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/05/03/php7m5AKN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F05%2F03%2Fphp7m5AKN.jpg&h=e1961338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖擷自@yRfEPnw6QZutzNg推特）<br />\n<br />\n果不其然，日本推特網友毫不留情地在下方留言批評，直說中國怎麼不畫一畫天安門事件，接著中方疑似刪除了推特文章，又引來了不少嘲諷，笑稱中國果然是個謊言連篇的國家。美國駐日大使館隨後也在推特發文，感謝日本網友對那則「令人不愉快的推文」發表看法。<br />\n<br />\n另外，推特一時之間也興起了修圖熱潮，將圖片改成披著中國國旗的死神，前面內蒙古、新疆、西藏、香港的門縫都流出鮮血，目前正在敲著台灣的大門；也有圖片修成只有台灣的門沒有血跡流出，象徵著我國在防堵中共方面做得很好，但如今中國正敲著世界的大門，可能全球各國都要小心了。"},{"pid":"e397b68fbec8ed0c7fa602dd32736b52b71e49d5","tid":2514380,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:33:37.000Z","msg":"happy share"},{"pid":"9d0a2256f7805af0531aedebbf69e1e9f031305a","tid":2514380,"uid":287891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:34:43.000Z","msg":"睇完嗰兩張改圖心情都舒服晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06643f08c2a744497a61069abcc920cf136a74a7","tid":2514380,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/05/03/phpK59TqR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F05%2F03%2FphpK59TqR.jpg&h=a0394cf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沖繩(琉球)之後到蒙古 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b2584d18beafe23a712a73bae93c1857485a84","tid":2514380,"uid":186608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}